<refsection condition='ref.description'>
<title>Description</title>


<para>A <tag>Step</tag> identifies a unit of action in a <tag>Procedure</tag>.
If a finer level of granularity is required for some steps, you
can embed <tag>SubSteps</tag> in a <tag>Step</tag>. Embedded 
<tag>SubSteps</tag> contain <tag>Step</tag>s, so that substeps can
be nested to any depth.
</para>

<refsection><title>Processing expectations</title>
<para><?tdg gentext='format.block'?>
<tag>Step</tag>s are almost always numbered.
</para>
